parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause the loss of safety features, including the rearview camera, autonomous emergency braking, and park distance control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The infotainment system fails to start or load
displays error messages such as "component protection active" or "you can activate this function at dealer"
and becomes inoperable
including the rearview camera
autonomous emergency braking
and park distance control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rearview camera can increase the risk of accidents and injuries, especially when reversing.
symptoms: The rearview camera does not turn on
freezes the image
or does not display an image at all.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the autonomous emergency braking system can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The autonomous emergency braking system fails to function
and the fail light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the park distance control system can increase the risk of accidents and injuries, especially when parking.
symptoms: The park distance control system fails to function
and the fail light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The low voltage issue can cause the infotainment system to malfunction, leading to the loss of safety features, including the rearview camera.
symptoms: The infotainment system displays a "low voltage" warning
and the system fails to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inaccurate navigation system can cause drivers to take wrong routes, leading to potential safety risks, such as accidents, getting lost, or driving into hazardous areas.
symptoms: The navigation system provides incorrect directions
the vehicle is directed to take wrong routes
the navigation system fails to update or correct its route
the navigation system freezes or becomes unresponsive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dealership to diagnose and repair the issue can lead to continued safety risks, driver frustration, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The dealership is unable to diagnose the issue
the dealership is unable to repair the issue
the dealership takes an excessive amount of time to repair the issue
the dealership fails to provide a satisfactory solution.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hill start assist feature can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents, especially in traffic situations and intersections.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when starting from a stop on a hill
the brake is not released when the vehicle starts moving forward
the clutch and gear engagement process is completed before the brakes are released.
